<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:wght@400;700&family=Lobster&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --header-height: 60px;
            --footer-height: 40px;
            --primary-color: #282c34;
            --accent-color: sandybrown;
            --link-hover: indianred;
            --button-blue: #007bff;
        }

        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        body {
            background-image: url('/css/image.png');
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            background-attachment: fixed;
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            color: white;
            font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
            padding-top: 180px;
            padding-bottom: 60px;
        }

        .header-container {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            background-color: var(--primary-color);
            padding: 10px;
            color: white;
            z-index: 1000;
            opacity: 0.95;
        }

        .logo h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            padding: 5px 0;
            font-family: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .nav-links {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 8px;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }

        .nav-links a {
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 10px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            background: var(--accent-color);
            border-radius: 6px;
            transition: 0.3s;
            text-align: center;
            display: block;
        }

        .nav-links a:hover {
            background: transparent;
            border: 1px solid var(--link-hover);
        }

        .content {
            width: 90%;
            margin: 15px auto;
            background-color: rgba(11, 9, 9, 0.8);
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow-y: auto;
            max-height: calc(100vh - 250px);
        }

        h2 {
            color: var(--accent-color);
            font-size: 1.4rem;
            margin: 20px 0 15px 0;
        }

        h3 {
            color: white;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            margin: 15px 0 10px 0;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 1rem;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        ul, ol {
            margin: 0 0 15px 20px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        li {
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            font-size: 1rem;
        }

        .contact-button {
            display: inline-block;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 10px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            background: var(--accent-color);
            border-radius: 6px;
            transition: 0.3s;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }

        .contact-button:hover {
            background: transparent;
            border: 1px solid var(--link-hover);
        }

        .footer {
            position: fixed;
            bottom: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            background-color: var(--primary-color);
            padding: 10px;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            opacity: 0.95;
        }

        /* Tablet styles (768px and up) */
        @media screen and (min-width: 768px) {
            body {
                padding-top: 100px;
            }

            .header-container {
                padding: 15px 30px;
            }

            .nav-links {
                flex-direction: row;
                justify-content: center;
                gap: 15px;
            }

            .nav-links a {
                padding: 8px 20px;
                font-size: 1.1rem;
            }

            .content {
                max-width: 700px;
                padding: 30px;
            }

            h2 {
                font-size: 1.8rem;
            }

            h3 {
                font-size: 1.4rem;
            }

            p, li {
                font-size: 1.2rem;
            }
        }

        /* Desktop styles (1024px and up) */
        @media screen and (min-width: 1024px) {
            .header-container {
                display: flex;
                justify-content: space-between;
                align-items: center;
                padding: 15px 50px;
            }

            .logo h1 {
                font-size: 2.8rem;
            }

            .nav-links {
                margin-top: 0;
            }

            .content {
                padding: 40px;
                margin-top: 30px;
            }

            p, li {
                font-size: 1.4rem;
            }
        }

        /* Touch device optimizations */
        @media (hover: none) {
            .nav-links a,
            .contact-button {
                padding: 12px 16px;
            }
        }

        /* Dark mode support */
        @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
            .header-container,
            .footer {
                background-color: #1a1a1a;
            }
        }

        /* High contrast mode */
        @media (prefers-contrast: high) {
            :root {
                --primary-color: #000000;
                --accent-color: #ff6b00;
                --link-hover: #ff0000;
                --button-blue: #0051ff;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header-container">
        <div class="logo">
            <h1>Help Center</h1>
        </div>
        <nav class="nav-links">
            <a href="#getting-started">Getting Started</a>
            <a href="#account">Account</a>
            <a href="#support">Support</a>
        </nav>
    </div>

    <main class="content">
        <section id="getting-started">
            <h2>Getting Started</h2>
            <h3>Creating Your Account</h3>
            <p>Follow these simple steps to get started:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Click the "Sign Up" button in the header</li>
                <li>Enter your email address</li>
                <li>Create a secure password</li>
                <li>Complete your profile information</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section id="account">
            <h2>Account Management</h2>
            <h3>Profile Settings</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Update your personal information</li>
                <li>Change password or security settings</li>
                <li>Manage email preferences</li>
                <li>Control privacy settings</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section id="support">
            <h2>Support</h2>
            <h3>Contact Us</h3>
            <p>Need help? Our support team is available 24/7.</p>
            <a href="mailto:support@example.com" class="contact-button">Email Support</a>
            <h3>Response Times</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Live Chat: Immediate assistance</li>
                <li>Email: Within 24 hours</li>
                <li>Phone: Less than 5 minute wait</li>
            </ul>
        </section>
    </main>

    <footer class="footer">
        <p>Â© 2024 Your Company Name. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>